	This DTD was modified for the Arbortext implementation.
      Changes:
      20030116 verstatpg attribute in entity docatt changed 
               from verified | unverified to ver | unver to match 38784BV6
      20030116 created three row wrappers for semantic tables:
                 cpinrow in cpintbl
                 consumrow in consumtbl
                 sptteqptrow in sptteqpttbl
               changed the contents of the related table to be the row wrapper, 
               and moved the contents into the new row wrapper element
      20040220 -Added %chgatt; to content models:
                  cpintbl
               - removed 38784 from this file and use entity reference
               - removed 38784 subset in favor of an entity to 38784 directory

      ********************************************************************** -->

